value.name: Duel of landscape gardener
value.overview: In this docutainment format, two garden professionals develop ideas for every garden and apply for the contract from the owners. Eva Brenner provides advice to the families.

value.name: A Landscape of Love
value.overview: Qin Hao, facing a career crisis, reunites with Lu Shiming, a former junior who left a high-paying job to return home and start a business. Together, they heal, find love, and work to revitalize the countryside.

value.name: Duel of landscape gardener - my green paradise
value.original_name: Duell der Gartenprofis - Mein grünes Paradies
value.overview: In this “Duel of landscape gardener”, the goal is to create a dream garden even with a small budget. Above all, personal initiative and professional support are necessary. In each episode, two garden and landscape builders present concepts for the conversion to a family. The focus is clearly on cheap alternatives to expensive building materials or plants. This shows how existing materials can be recycled. Under the guidance of the garden professional, whose concept is preferred by the owners, the family is actively involved in the renovation.

value.name: Geo Japan: 100 Amazing Landscapes
value.original_name: ジオ・ジャパン 絶景100の旅
value.overview: Uncovering the secrets of the birth of stunning natural landscapes in Japan, where the earth's dynamic forces have sculpted some of the most captivating vistas on the planet. Featuring on-location footage, expert insights, and CG animations, the show brings Japan’s geological wonders to life and deepens our understanding of the geological processes.

value.name: Landscape of Pain
value.overview: In a shabby neighborhood where serial murders are disguised as lonely deaths occur, an elderly priest who hears the confession of a criminal and a middle-aged female detective work together to find and chase down the culprit.
